{"tid":2089169,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴基斯坦分離組織不滿中國藉「一帶一路」掠資源","createTime":"2020-07-01T13:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T14:00:03.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c0f3a2d42665817c031c4da8fb18bf0b1d5afe","tid":2089169,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦卡拉奇的證券交易所昨日遇襲，四名持手榴彈及自動步槍的槍手闖入亂槍掃射，最少七人死亡，包括一名警察和四名保安，另外七人受傷。到場的特警與槍手駁火擊斃他們。武裝組織「俾路支解放軍」（BLA）事後承認施襲。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\nBLA在資源豐富的俾路支省戰鬥多年，不滿巴基斯坦西南部省分的天然氣和礦產資源分配不公，指中國掠奪俾路支資源，中資工程不公平地開發區內礦物和碳氫化合物資源，近年多次針對基建工程和華工發動襲擊。BLA前年承認襲擊中國駐卡拉奇大使館，造成四死。去年5月，BLA襲擊「中巴經濟走廊」終點瓜達爾（Gwadar）一間五星級酒店，造成至少五死六傷。BLA當時承認是針對中國投資者發動攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何巴基斯坦不定立巴基國安法讓 巴基斯坦經濟重新出發、止暴制亂，重回正軌， 確保社會穩定及維持企業信心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200630/5AWKP2AHQAU44NLEZ5X2SH6TII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200630%2F5AWKP2AHQAU44NLEZ5X2SH6TII&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9ZS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=21fbe6f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200630%2F5AWKP2AHQAU44NLEZ5X2SH6TII&h=c8d05f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200630/5AWKP2AHQAU44NLEZ5X2SH6TII</a>"},{"pid":"84dcd2fdb8e7628ced962e3cf1729403f5d10018","tid":2089169,"uid":299514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"解放軍對解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}